Create conda virtual environment:
(base) Prashants-MBP:lifetime-value shinde$ conda env create --name py17_pnbd --file environment.yml

List all conda environments:
(base) Prashants-MBP:lifetime-value shinde$ conda env list 

Activate virtual environment:
(base) Prashants-MBP:lifetime-value shinde$ conda activate py17_pnbd
(py17_pnbd) Prashants-MBP:lifetime-value shinde$ 

Deactivate virtual environment:
(py17_pnbd) Prashants-MBP:lifetime-value shinde$ conda deactivate
(base) Prashants-MBP:lifetime-value shinde$ 


